description: The Potato Coop is cutting up fresh cut potato fries and making the signature "Corkscrew" hot dogs , offering the best lunch bite in Harrisburg, PA. You can never have enough of the fries with option of flavors Cajun, Taco, Old Bay or just Plain. The "Corkscrew" hot dog a definite appetite opener, you are sure to make your belly happy. To make it a greater meal you can make it a combo which adds chicken tenders to your epic meal. You can also book the Potato Coop for your next big event ,you are sure to satisfy all your guest!
name: The Potato Coop
